      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VICTORY EXAM (1) is still a maiden after 12 runs but rarely out of the placings, the latest filling a minor again when fourth at this track. Looks the one to beat on his best form. BOLD ASSAIL (7) has been in the frame at his last two runs, most recently when third (30.56) in a Maiden over 515m at Sandown. Can improve sharply here. ASTON MACHINE (8) drifted back from wide but charged home to hit the frame when 5.5 lengths from the winner (25.69) at Ballarat in Maiden. The form out of last race has been strong. Can feature again. FULL BORE DONNY (5) makes debut for the Peter Inguanti kennel. Start all important. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
